Package: ecmei
Title: Lattice-based models   
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c( person("Jae", "Choi", email="choijaeseok@gmail.com", role=c("aut", "cre")) ) 
Description: Lattice-based models -- Constrained Kernel-based methods of modelling and predicting space-time hierarchical models. This package interacts with bio and associated projects to provide some kernel-density like (global covariate modelling - local space-time windowed) modelling and interpolation methods. Constrainst are in the form of covariates and/or local process models.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), 
  mvtnorm, 
  truncnorm
